.TP
\f[B]PKGD_OUTPUT_VERBOSE\f[R]
Enable verbose output by default.
.TP
\f[B]PKGD_OUTPUT_COLOR\f[R]
Set to \f[B]false\f[R] to disable colored output (overridden by
